data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch home! It features a large fenced yard with a playset and shed to store all your garden gear. Inside, enjoy over 1600 sqft of space, with an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings and newer LVP flooring in the living room, and plenty of storage. The kitchen boasts granite countertops and tile backsplash. Plus, you can enjoy the view of the community pond and geese from your front door and the community pool and playground just down the street. Schedule your tour today!
